{"tid":1569714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《救跳閘仔女須知》","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T18:06:27.000Z","uid":226059,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"957d21dc0c5a15f9fe094fcbab67daa872bb40fd","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"今日喺黨鐵站救咗一位跳閘嘅仔女，好感動同場有好幾位手足，一見到有仔女畀人捉咗，都不約而同即刻衝咗上去救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後佢哋成功走甩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前喺Facebook見到有人列出一啲法理依據，等各位手足可以更順利救人，我覺得幾有用所以簡單整合咗，希望share出去，等多啲人知道我哋救人<strong>係合情合理合法！</strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：<strong>我絕非作者或法律界人士</strong>，只係無恥地偷咗原文兼整合一下，希望更多人睇到！同時，<strong>如果有任何錯咗嘅地方，歡迎大大力屌柒我</strong>，等大家唔好好似我咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《救跳閘仔女須知》<br />\n<br />\n─ 唔係佢話人跳閘就係<br />\n─ 跳閘最高刑罰僅$5,000，並非「可逮捕罪行（arrestable offence）」 ，<strong>捉人跳閘者冇權行使公民逮捕權（休班警都冇權）</strong><br />\n─ 承上，相反佢唔畀人走，<strong>已犯非法禁錮罪</strong><br />\n─ 非法禁錮最高可判7年，變相各熱心市民可以<strong>行使公民逮捕權，逮捕呢位捉人跳閘嘅柒頭</strong><br />\n<br />\n─────<br />\n法 理 依 據<br />\n<br />\n─ <ins>「公民逮捕權」</ins><br />\n根據《基本法》<br />\n第221章《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條：<br />\n<em>「任何人可<strong>無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人。</strong>」</em><br />\n<br />\n─<ins>「可逮捕的罪行」定義：</ins><br />\n<em>指由法律規固定刑罰的罪行，或根據、憑藉法例對犯者<strong>可處超過12個月監禁的罪行</strong>，亦指犯任何這類罪行的企圖 。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s 大大聲屈鳩佢摸人，扮幫手錯開佢去叫站務員，然後承機放人呢啲，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好做呀</span></span>，知唔知道？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一圖過，方便share&amp;save：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWvedKR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWvedKR.png&h=019203db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2670648152959551?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F937160302975020%2Fposts%2F2670648152959551%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=e1cda87a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2670648152959551?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0c596bb8dbd71a10e0e0c71d4a1c33ccdafebec6","tid":1569714,"uid":306354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"推呀 大家識做啦"},{"pid":"287de8c9972f788714704f29b2d367d599317357","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（1/10）"},{"pid":"5d39dbaad00b67fc3b4e4ea939e63bbad76e1729","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（2/10）"},{"pid":"bc38355d8186de557c22ac66720e1b8807336fba","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（3/10）"},{"pid":"56d5bbcbf6dbfaabf1b9575921e3aec70f141dec","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（4/10）"},{"pid":"b67c455a84316ba65a0ce34d7f53baaa3e55ea7d","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（5/10）"},{"pid":"d893ab90fa2695086f4451dfffae823632aea927","tid":1569714,"uid":226059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"